lxd (2.1-0ubuntu4) yakkety; urgency=medium

  * Fix powerpc build by using golang-any-shared-dev instead of
    golang-go-shared-dev.

 -- Stéphane Graber <stgraber@ubuntu.com>  Thu, 08 Sep 2016 17:39:41 -0400

