  * Update previous patch to remove any related code as otherwise the
    static analysis run in the testsuite (shellcheck) will fail on unused
    variables.

 -- Stéphane Graber <stgraber@ubuntu.com>  Sun, 01 Nov 2015 00:10:16 -0400

